## Stack

| Component | Tool | Notes |
|-----------|------|-------|
| PDF extraction | PyMuPDF (fitz) | with pdfplumber fallback |
| Chunking | LangChain RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter | |
| Embedding model | BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5 | First choice, ~130MB, MIT license |
| | BAAI/bge-base-en-v1.5 | Alternative, ~440MB, higher quality |
| Reranker | BAAI/bge-reranker-base | Cross-encoder reranking |
| Vector database | pgvector (PostgreSQL) | Production backend on Nuvolos |
| | ChromaDB | Local development backend |
| | FAISS | In-memory alternative for comparison |
| LLM | Qwen2.5-7B-Instruct | First choice, Apache 2.0, no access request needed |
| | Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3 | Alternative, requires HuggingFace license acceptance |
| Backend API | FastAPI + uvicorn | Hosted on Nuvolos Backend instance |
| Frontend | Streamlit | Hosted on Nuvolos Frontend instance |
| Deployment | Nuvolos | 3-tier: Frontend → Backend → Database, plus Trainer T4 (GPU) for the LLM |

See [`NUVOLOS_DEPLOYMENT.md`](NUVOLOS_DEPLOYMENT.md) for the full deployment architecture and step-by-step setup.

